messages.message: Hey, it's nice to meet you in person finally, Olivia told me so much about you. I'm so glad she has someone like you.
Hey, it's good to meet you too! I'm the one who's grateful for her!
You got Olivia a lot of nice clothes and bags. It must be very expensive, what do you do for work?
NEW MATERIAL POSSESSIONS ARE AN INDICATOR OF TRAFFICKING
If you're 19 and you're not in college, do you have a job?
Yeah, I work as an entrepreneur.
Oh? What's your line of business?.
It's complicated, so we shouldn't get into it, but it's allowed me to spoil Olivia.
You must really care about Olivia to be getting her so much.
What can I say, Olivia means the most to me.
So tell me how you got into lacrosse.
Lacrosse?
Isn't that what you and Olivia connected over...
Yeah, you mentioned it when we talked on Finsta.
He’s just tired from his work. His dad taught him when he was a little kid.
Oh alright, what about-
Why don’t we talk about you, we’ve talked about Jack so much.
Yeah, let’s do that. I'd love to know more about you and Olivia’s friendship.
Yeah sure, I just wanted to get to know you for Olivia's sake.
I'm just making sure you’re good enough for Olivia, I’m a little protective over her.
Well that makes sense, no one is good enough for Olivia, I’m just grateful she chose me. Olivia, can we talk for a second?
Yeah, um, sure. Is everything fine?
Yeah, of course. In private though... Be right back.
